<!-- TODO: update once the CLI commands are implemented -->

## Database Management

```bash
# Stop the database (data is preserved)
docker compose down

# Stop and wipe all data (re-runs init scripts on next start)
docker compose down -v

# View database logs
docker compose logs db
```


